# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OPTIONAL — advanced only. The course path uses Claude Cowork with your
# Claude.ai subscription: no API key, no .env, no terminal. See README.md.
# These settings only matter if you run the optional Python script (main.py)
# yourself. No ANTHROPIC_API_KEY is needed anywhere here.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Path to the primary source CSV (authoritative data)
SOURCE_A=source_a.csv

# Path to the secondary/destination CSV (gets rows appended)
SOURCE_B=source_b.csv

# Column name used as the unique identifier / primary key
ID_COLUMN=id

# Log file path
LOG_FILE=run.log

# Delta log (JSON Lines) -- one record per sync run
DELTA_LOG=delta_log.jsonl
